{
  "id": "adv_event_2111_01_03",
  "title": "託された想い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "このタイミングで、ターン……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And a turn right here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7333333333,
      "endTime": 5.2999999999666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、新曲の振り付け、なんとかなりそう\nあとは、芽衣と合わせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ looks like the choreography for the new song is coming together.\nNow I have to coordinate it with Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0666666667,
      "endTime": 16.099999999966666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "遅いな、芽衣。もう練習開始の時間、過ぎてるのに\nもしかして、何かあったんじゃ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei’s late. It’s already past the beginning of practice time.\nI wonder if something happened to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2666666667,
      "endTime": 24.966666666699997,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3600.0000000000014
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、お待たせ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan! Sorry for keeping you waiting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1666666667,
      "endTime": 28.7333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.666666599999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、遅刻よ。心配させないで\nほら、早く着替えて……あれ、どうしてすずも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re late‚ Mei. You make me worried.\nGet changed quickly… Oh‚ why is Suzu here too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9666666667,
      "endTime": 39.166666666699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンの前に聞いてほしいことがありますわ！\n怜にとって大切なことですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s something we want you to hear before the lesson.\nIt’s really important for you‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "endTime": 46.633333331500005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ。レッスンが先\n新ユニットのお披露目ライブまで時間がないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope. The lesson comes first.\nWe don’t have enough time before the launch concert for our new team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8333333333,
      "endTime": 54.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "期間限定のユニット活動だからって\n無様なライブは見せられないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can’t put on an ungainly show‚\njust because this is temporary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4666666667,
      "endTime": 59.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ、すぐ着替えるから一言だけ聞いて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it. Just listen for a moment before I get changed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7666666667,
      "endTime": 64.00000000003334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "もう、どうしたのよ？\nそんなに慌てて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is this all about?\nWhy are you getting so worked up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2,
      "endTime": 68.36666666663332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "怜とお父様の話し合いの場を\nセッティングしましたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We set up an opportunity for you\nto talk with your father!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5666666667,
      "endTime": 72.60000000003333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8,
      "endTime": 73.66000000238418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "――という訳で、芽衣達\n怜ちゃんの実家に行ってきたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What she means is‚ we’ve just been\nto your parents’ house.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9666666667,
      "endTime": 80.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "……はあ、勝手なことを……芽衣らしいけど\nどうせ相手にされなかったんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s just like you to butt in like that‚ Mei.\nHe couldn’t have cared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7,
      "endTime": 88.76666666663334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、お仕事が忙しいんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ he said he was busy with work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9666666667,
      "endTime": 92.63333333336665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、怜ちゃんにはもっと人の助けになるお仕事に\nついてほしいって言ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ your father said he wanted you to do a job\nthat helped people a lot more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8333333333,
      "endTime": 100.03333333336666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "……変わらないわね。アイドルの仕事のこと\n何も分かってない。いえ、分かろうともしないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Same old thing. He doesn’t understand\nthe idol’s job at all. No‚ he doesn’t even try to understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2333333333,
      "endTime": 109.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 109.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ！　ですから、私が熱く語ろうとしたら\n芽衣が止めるんですのよ！　まったく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! So when I tried to talk to him from the heart‚\nMei went and stopped me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3666666667,
      "endTime": 117.46666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、止めるでしょ～。普通あれは止めるよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ everyone would have. Everyone would‚ normally!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6333333333,
      "endTime": 122.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣に「普通」って言われると\nなんだか腑に落ちませんわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It just doesn’t sound right when\nyou use the word “normal”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0333333333,
      "endTime": 128.43333333329997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "……あのね。あなた達、火に油を注ぎに行ったの？\nそんなことしたって、ライブに来る訳ないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ why did you two go to pour fuel on the fire?\nDoing something like that won’t get him to come to a live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6333333333,
      "endTime": 136.89999999996667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ。その後、私達が帰る途中\n怜のお母様が追っていらしたんですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ after that‚ Rei's mother caught up with us‚\nas we were heading home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0666666667,
      "endTime": 143.43333333336665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、優しいお母さんだね\n芽衣達のお話、ちゃんと聞いてくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your mum’s really kind.\nShe listened properly to what we said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6333333333,
      "endTime": 150.76666666670002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お母さんはお父さんには逆らわない……\n私の味方にはなってくれない人なのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she won’t go against my father…\nShe’s someone who won’t stand on my side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9666666667,
      "endTime": 158.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "……そんな風に決めつけずに、もう少し\nお母様の言葉に耳を傾けるべきじゃありませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rather than making up your mind like that‚\nhow about listening a little more to what your mother had to say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8,
      "endTime": 165.70000000003336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 165.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
